snippet.title: Thank you for the support! Control Accolades Trailer
snippet.description:
Our community and critics have spoken!

On behalf of everyone at Remedy Entertainment and 505 Games, thank you for the support you've shown Control.

Vote for Control in #TheGameAwards: https://thegameawards.com/nominees
